<body>

<div1 xml:lang="en" type="document">

<pb n="Roll6-3116.jpg"/>

<note>Index Bureau Dept. of State Recd. Nov 2 '00</note>

<p>No. 48. Consular.<lb/>
Legation of the United States.<lb/>
Monrovia Liberia;<lb/>
Sept. 19, 1900.</p>

<p>Hon. David J. Hill,<lb/>
Assistant Secretary of State,<lb/>
Washington.</p>

<p>Subject.</p>

<p>Gas Engines.</p>

<p>Synopsis.</p>

<p>No Gas Engines in Liberia.
All kind of machinery, sewing
machines, agricultural <sic>emplements</sic>,
and tools free of duty.</p>
    
</div1>

